[
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked person</st> <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">fled</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> though <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> one was <st data-num=\"07291\" class=\"\">pursuing</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">righteous person</st> can <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">be</st> as <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">confident</st><n id=\"3\" /> as a <st data-num=\"03715\" class=\"\">lion</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">When a <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">country</st> is <st data-num=\"06588\" class=\"\">rebellious</st><n id=\"1\" /> it has <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">princes</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but by <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">someone</st> who is <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">discerning</st> and <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">knowledgeable</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">order</st> is <st data-num=\"0748\" class=\"\">maintained</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"07326\" class=\"\">poor</st> <st data-num=\"01397\" class=\"\">person</st><n id=\"1\" /> who <st data-num=\"06231\" class=\"\">oppresses</st> the <st data-num=\"01800\" class=\"\">weak</st><p class=\"poetry\">is like<n id=\"2\" /> a <st data-num=\"05502\" class=\"\">driving</st> <st data-num=\"04306\" class=\"\">rain</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">without</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Those who <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">forsake</st> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">praise</st> the <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but those who <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">keep</st> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> <st data-num=\"01624\" class=\"\">contend</st><n id=\"3\" /> with them.</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">Evil</st> <st data-num=\"0582\" class=\"\">people</st><n id=\"1\" /> do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understand</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but those who <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">seek</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understand</st> it <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"07326\" class=\"\">poor person</st><n id=\"1\" /> who <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">walks</st> in his <st data-num=\"08537\" class=\"\">integrity</st> is <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">better</st><p class=\"poetry\">than one who is <st data-num=\"06141\" class=\"\">perverse</st> in his <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">ways</st><n id=\"2\" /> even though<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> is <st data-num=\"06223\" class=\"\">rich</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"05341\" class=\"\">keeps</st> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st><n id=\"1\" /> is a <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">discerning</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">child</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but a <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">companion</st> of <st data-num=\"02151\" class=\"\">gluttons</st> <st data-num=\"03637\" class=\"\">brings shame to</st><n id=\"3\" /> his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">parents</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">increases</st> his <st data-num=\"01952\" class=\"\">wealth</st> by <st data-num=\"08636\" class=\"\">increasing</st> <st data-num=\"05392\" class=\"\">interest</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">gathers</st> it for someone who is <st data-num=\"02603\" class=\"\">gracious</st><n id=\"2\" /> to the <st data-num=\"01800\" class=\"\">needy</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"05493\">turns away</st> his <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">ear</st><n id=\"1\" /> from <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hearing</st> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">even</st> his <st data-num=\"08605\" class=\"\">prayer</st><n id=\"2\" /> is an <st data-num=\"08441\" class=\"\">abomination</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"07686\" class=\"\">leads</st> the <st data-num=\"03477\" class=\"\">upright</st> <st data-num=\"07686\" class=\"\">astray</st> in an <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st><p class=\"poetry\">will <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">himself</st> <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fall</st> into his own <st data-num=\"07816\" class=\"\">pit</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but the <st data-num=\"08549\" class=\"\">blameless</st> will <st data-num=\"05157\" class=\"\">inherit</st> <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">what is good</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"06223\" class=\"\">rich</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">person</st><n id=\"1\" /> is <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">wise</st> in his own <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">opinion</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but a <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">discerning</st> <st data-num=\"01800\" class=\"\">poor person</st> can <st data-num=\"02713\" class=\"\">evaluate</st> him <st data-num=\"02713\" class=\"\">properly</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">When the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">righteous</st> <st data-num=\"05970\" class=\"\">rejoice</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">great</st> is the <st data-num=\"08597\" class=\"\">glory</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but when the <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">rise to power</st>, <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">people</st> are <st data-num=\"02664\" class=\"\">sought out</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"03680\" class=\"\">covers</st><n id=\"1\" /> his <st data-num=\"06588\" class=\"\">transgressions</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06743\" class=\"\">prosper</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but whoever <st data-num=\"03034\" class=\"\">confesses</st> them and <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">forsakes</st> them will <st data-num=\"07355\" class=\"\">find mercy</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0835\" class=\"\">Blessed</st> is the <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">one</st> who is <st data-num=\"08548\" class=\"\">always</st> <st data-num=\"06342\" class=\"\">cautious</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but whoever <st data-num=\"07185\" class=\"\">hardens</st> his <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fall</st> into <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Like<n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"05098\" class=\"\">roaring</st> <st data-num=\"0738\" class=\"\">lion</st> or a <st data-num=\"08264\" class=\"\">roving</st> <st data-num=\"01677\" class=\"\">bear</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">so is a <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked</st> <st data-num=\"04910\" class=\"\">ruler</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> a <st data-num=\"01800\" class=\"\">poor</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"05057\" class=\"\">prince</st> who is a <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"04642\" class=\"\">oppressor</st> <st data-num=\"02638\" class=\"\">lacks</st> <st data-num=\"08394\" class=\"\">wisdom</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but the one who <st data-num=\"08130\" class=\"\">hates</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"01215\" class=\"\">unjust gain</st> will <st data-num=\"0748\" class=\"\">prolong</st> his <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">one</st> who is <st data-num=\"06231\" class=\"\">tormented</st><n id=\"1\" /> by the <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">murder</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">another</st> will <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">flee</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"0953\" class=\"\">pit</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">let <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">no</st> one <st data-num=\"08551\" class=\"\">support</st> him.</p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">walks</st> <st data-num=\"08549\" class=\"\">blamelessly</st> will be <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">delivered</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but whoever is <st data-num=\"06140\" class=\"\">perverse</st> in his <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">ways</st> will <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fall</st><n id=\"2\" /> at <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">once</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">works</st> his <st data-num=\"0127\" class=\"\">land</st> will <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">be satisfied</st> with <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but whoever <st data-num=\"07291\" class=\"\">chases</st> <st data-num=\"07386\" class=\"\">daydreams</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">have</st> his <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">fill</st><n id=\"3\" /> of <st data-num=\"07389\" class=\"\">poverty</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"0530\" class=\"\">faithful</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">person</st><n id=\"1\" /> will have an <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">abundance</st> of <st data-num=\"01293\" class=\"\">blessings</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but the one who <st data-num=\"0213\" class=\"\">hastens</st><n id=\"2\" /> to <st data-num=\"06238\" class=\"\">gain riches</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05352\" class=\"\">go unpunished</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">To <st data-num=\"05234\" class=\"\">show</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">partiality</st><n id=\"1\" /> is <st data-num=\"03808 02896\">terrible</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">for a <st data-num=\"01397\" class=\"\">person</st> will <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">transgress</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> the <st data-num=\"06595\" class=\"\">smallest piece</st> of <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">bread</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07451 05869\">stingy</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">person</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0926\" class=\"\">hastens</st> after <st data-num=\"01952\" class=\"\">riches</st><p class=\"poetry\">and does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"02639\" class=\"\">poverty</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">overtake</st> him.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"03198\" class=\"\">reproves</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">another</st><n id=\"2\" /> will in the <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">end</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">find</st> more <st data-num=\"02580\" class=\"\">favor</st><p class=\"poetry\">than the one who <st data-num=\"02505\" class=\"\">flatters</st><n id=\"4\" /> with the <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">tongue</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"01497\" class=\"\">robs</st><n id=\"1\" /> his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st> and <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mother</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">There is no</st> <st data-num=\"06588\" class=\"\">transgression</st>,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">is</st> a <st data-num=\"02270\" class=\"\">companion</st><n id=\"2\" /> to the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st><n id=\"3\" /> who <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroys</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07342\" class=\"\">greedy</st> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">person</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01624\" class=\"\">stirs up</st> <st data-num=\"04066\" class=\"\">dissension</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but the one who <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">trusts</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"01878\" class=\"\">prosper</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">trusts</st> in his own <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">is</st> a <st data-num=\"03684\" class=\"\">fool</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but the <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">one</st> who <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">walks</st> in <st data-num=\"02451\" class=\"\">wisdom</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">escape</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The one who <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">gives</st> to the <st data-num=\"07326\" class=\"\">poor</st> will <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04270\" class=\"\">lack</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but whoever <st data-num=\"05956\" class=\"\">shuts</st> his <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> to them<n id=\"2\" /> will receive<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"03994\" class=\"\">curses</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Proverbs",
    "chapter": "28",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">When the <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">gain control</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">people</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05641\" class=\"\">hide</st> themselves,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but when they <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">perish</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">righteous</st> <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">increase</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  }
]